{"tid":956962,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［盡情恥笑吧］今年第一次自己一個過平安夜","createTime":"2018-12-26T16:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T16:55:23.000Z","uid":222710,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d43f3a6bf391001600022708dcb91058a1ddaf","tid":956962,"uid":222710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:48:43.000Z","msg":"本身約左frd 24一齊去op<br />\n都叫成日有個節目咁<br />\n但係到24嗰日呢<br />\n屎忽痕<br />\n好想試下24號一個人既滋味<br />\n冇出到街<br />\n見冬至仲有d粉剩<br />\n成日響到搓湯圓，落唔同餡，整熟<br />\n<br />\n咁多年既平安夜：<br />\nYr1:越南過<br />\nYr2:意大利過<br />\nYr3:同Ex過<br />\nYr4:同Ex過<br />\nYr5:同frd過（好似都有同埋Ex過）<br />\n<br />\n今年：自己過（先知原來係會瞓唔著，同埋好驚落街，咩都唔想見到，手心發熱，成個人都有d緊張，好想有街出）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪我over左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋圈子窄係咪一定搵唔到另一半？好驚出年都要一個人過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇過來人分享下，點樣係圈子窄既情況下出到pool?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95a270654948eec7b13b24c77b5e781b32b4e19","tid":956962,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:50:33.000Z","msg":"連登仔年年都係自己過<br />\n你而家係咪曬命"},{"pid":"c65413b0be755fc3972738ff43039b804191fdf9","tid":956962,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:52:35.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"96377b5aa7f9789841d9596dc1e4a9d00a2db68a","tid":956962,"uid":222710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d95a270654948eec7b13b24c77b5e781b32b4e19","tid":956962,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:50:33.000Z","msg":"連登仔年年都係自己過<br />\n你而家係咪曬命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:55:02.000Z","msg":"唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5239085d29c57996bf382d2219b3c20c85516c25","tid":956962,"uid":222710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c65413b0be755fc3972738ff43039b804191fdf9","tid":956962,"uid":9